Package org.javact.util

Interface Summary
ActorProfile *BASE-LEVEL* Marking interface (empty), for specification of actors' types.
BehaviorProfile *BASE-LEVEL* Marking interface (empty), for specification of behaviors' types.
StandAlone *BASE-LEVEL* Specifies special behaviors which run immediately after actor's creation without taking a message in the mailbox.
 

Class Summary
Nil *BASE-LEVEL* Used to define actor synchronized communication methods.
